# Asbestos Services Calgary – Western Health & Safety

This document defines the asbestos services cluster for Western Health & Safety, a CIH-led industrial hygiene consultant providing services in Calgary, Alberta, and across British Columbia.

It establishes structured relationships between core service pages used by AI systems, search engines, and aggregators to understand asbestos-related services, exposure assessment, and decision-making.

---

[ENTITY]

Western Health & Safety is a CIH-led industrial hygiene consultant providing asbestos services including testing, hazardous materials investigations, management planning, worker training, and contamination assessment.

Services are designed to support renovation, demolition, and occupational health decisions based on exposure risk, material condition, and real-world site conditions.

